Package HMS.Models

Class AppointmentOutcomeRecord

java.lang.Object
HMS.Models.AppointmentOutcomeRecord
public class AppointmentOutcomeRecord extends Object
Represents the outcome of a completed appointment, including details like service type, prescribed medications, and consultation notes.
